&lt;p&gt;Its also possible with a simple &lt;code&gt;for&lt;/code&gt; loop:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-js s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-javascript&quot;&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; result = {};

 &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; {make, model, year} &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;of&lt;/span&gt; cars) {
   &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;(!result[make]) result[make] = [];
   result[make].&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title function_&quot;&gt;push&lt;/span&gt;({ model, year });
 }
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d leave &lt;code&gt;REAL GROUP BY&lt;/code&gt; for JS Arrays example exactly the same this task &lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/a/52797477/4882514&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

